  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span> is readily extracted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">underwater rock deposits</span>.<br>Increase marine efficiency by upgrading the Exosuit <span class=\"name name-technology\">Aeration Membrane</span> or by refilling oxygen supplies from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Kelp Sacs</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从<span class=\"name name-earth\">地下岩石矿床</span>中容易提取出<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>。<br>升级套装<span class=\"name name-technology\">换气薄膜</span>或从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TencentChinese": "从<span class=\"name name-earth\">地下岩石矿床</span>中容易提取出<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>。<br>升级套装<span class=\"name name-technology\">换气薄膜</span>或从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>可直接從<span class=\"name name-earth\">水底岩石資源產地</span>取得。<br>透過強化套裝升級<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝氣黏膜</span>或從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">巨藻囊</span>補充氧氣來源以提升海洋效能。"
  },
